    "attributes": {
        "action": "Owners to be able to claim compensation for pet suffering due to vet negligence",
        "additional_details": "Pets are sentient beings, yet the law treats them as property when harmed by a vet\u2019s mistake. We want better protections and justice for all animals.",
        "background": "We want a law allowing pet owners to claim legal damages for pain and suffering caused by veterinary negligence, holding vets accountable in court \u2014 not just for financial loss, but for the animal\u2019s suffering.",
